high_descs: Walk up to the ottoman on the left.
Pick up the hammer in front of the kettle on the ottoman.
Turn around and walk left to exit the room on the right and walk down the passage and reach the kitchen on the right and reach the cabinet under the sink.
Put the hammer in the cabinet.
Walk to the left down the passage and reach the room at the end to find the ottoman.
Pick up the hammer on the ottoman.
Turn around and walk left to exit the room on the right and walk down the passage and reach the kitchen on the right and reach the cabinet under the sink.
Put the hammer in the cabinet with the other hammer.
anns.task_desc: Put two Hammer in the Cabinet.

high_descs: Go to the ottoman ahead of you in the corner of the room.
Pick up the nearest hammer.
Turn right, go around the coffee table and go ahead before turning right into the hallway, then right again into the kitchen area, towards the cabinet.
Place the hammer into the cabinet beneath the sink.
Return to the ottoman where you got the hammer.
Pick up the second hammer.
Return to the cabinet you put the first hammer in.
Place the second hammer into the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place two hammers into a kitchen cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around the right side ottoman.
Take the hammer on the tool.
Then turn around on the cabinet.
Put the hammer on the cabinet in the cupboard room.
Then go to the ottoman on the left side.
Go to the hammer room.
Then take it on the cabinet.
Put the hammer on the cabinet in the cupboard room.
anns.task_desc: Take the hammer and put it in the cabinet.
